      <div class="msgContentFrame">Why does the game keep moving me closer to the target whenever I do any attacks? <br /> <br />I don't know about you but I've never NOT ended up in the mobs face; no matter how hard I try to stay in the medium range circle. I take these big leaps forward when I attack; making it impossible for me to keep a stable range. This is really frustrating if you want to set up skewer/pierce/doomspike consistantly. Also, due to this if I where to initiate a fight without lock on, the target will inevitably end up behind me. Makes no sense whatsoever. <br /> <br /> <br />Stop. Moving. Me!</div>
